'''大衛·巴利·"戴夫"·傑臣'''（{{lang-en|'''David Barry "Dave" Kitson'''}}，{{bd|1980年|1月21日|catidx=Kitson, Dave}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員，擔任[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，身材高大兼有一頭[[紅髮|紅髮]]，在場上非常容易辨認，於2014年宣佈退出職業球員行列。

==生平==
===剑桥联===
傑臣在萊奇沃思花園城（Letchworth Garden City）成長，於18歲時他曾放棄在家鄉球隊[[希欽鎮足球會|希治]]（Hitchin Town）繼續參賽，專注於其日間工作，在全國連鎖超市[[森寶利|森寶利]]任職急凍食品理貨員。他業餘時與朋友在當地週日聯賽參賽，擔任中堅，其後獲推薦到[[阿勒塞鎮足球會|阿尼斯城]]（Arlesey Town）試訓獲得接納，由於隊中首席前鋒受重傷，初來步到的傑臣因而改踢前鋒。在一場對[[剑桥联足球俱乐部|剑桥联]]預備隊的賽事被對方發掘並邀請簽約加盟。2001年3月17日傑臣為劍橋聯首次上陣出戰[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]，其後一直保持有上陣，直到球季煞科日作客[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:斯旺西;zh-hk:史雲斯}-]]頂入其首個入球<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.11v11.com/api/player/14392 |title=Dave Kitson |publisher=11v11.com |date= |accessdate=2009-11-18}}</ref></small>，他為劍橋聯上陣102場及射入40球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/reading/article2848048.ece |title=Shooting from the lip |work=[[The_Times|The Times]] |date=2007-11-11 |accessdate=2009-11-18 }}</ref></small>。

===雷丁===
[[File:Dave_Kitson.JPG|thumb]]
2003年12月26日傑臣以15萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]被賣到[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]<small><ref>{{cite news|language=en |url=http://www.cambridge-news.co.uk/sport/football/united/2006/03/27/b683caf1-e46e-45ef-8cf9-b6de50f1c4c5.lpf |title=Cash Point! |work=Cambridge Evening News |date=2006-03-27 |accessdate=2006-05-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060509101728/http://www.cambridge-news.co.uk/sport/football/united/2006/03/27/b683caf1-e46e-45ef-8cf9-b6de50f1c4c5.lpf |archivedate=2006-05-09 }}</ref></small>。他首季為雷丁效力在僅10場正選上陣即射入5球。2004/05年球季傑臣雖因受傷而缺陣一段時間，但他上陣38場射入19球，入球比率高達兩場入1球。翌年他維持高入球比率，上陣40場射入22球，而雷丁亦贏得[[英冠|英冠]]冠軍升班[[英超|英超]]。

傑臣隨同雷丁升班到[[英超|英超]]作賽，比3年前離開劍橋聯時連升了三級。他在[[2006年至2007年英格蘭超級聯賽|新球季]]揭幕日主場3-2擊敗[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]，射入雷丁在英超歷來首個入球，但卻遭受重創半場退下火線<small><ref>{{cite news|language=en |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~885161,00.html |title=Royals come back from two-nil down to beat Boro in first ever Premiership match |work=readingfc.co.uk |date=2006-08-19 |accessdate=2007-02-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080927141613/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10306~885161%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-09-27 }}</ref></small>，這次受傷使他一直缺陣，直到2007年1月27日雷丁在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]淘汰[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]才告復出<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~971508,00.html |title=Royals progress to the fifth round after good away win against Blues |work=readingfc.co.uk |date=2007-01-27 |accessdate=2007-02-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120805102750/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~971508,00.html |archivedate=2012-08-05 }}</ref></small>。3月27日傑臣將未來付託給雷丁，動筆簽署三年新約，直到2010年6月才屆滿<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-03-27 |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1002595,00.html |title=Kitson signs new three-year contract |work=readingfc.co.uk |accessdate=2007-03-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120805131426/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1002595,00.html |archivedate=2012-08-05 }}</ref></small>。但他的首個英超球季僅上陣18場，分別在聯賽及[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]各取得兩個入球。

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭超級聯賽|2007/08年球季]]揭幕戰作客對[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]，傑臣下半場72分鐘後補入替[[凯文·道尔|凯文·道尔]]，僅1分鍾便因攔截[[帕特里斯·埃夫拉|艾拉]]而遭球證出示[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場。2007年12月1日主場1-1賽和[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7110962.stm |title=Reading 1-1 Middlesbrough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-12-01 |accessdate=2009-11-18 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309144743/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7110962.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，他先拔頭籌的入球是他為雷丁射入的第37球，使他成雷丁歷來首席射手<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/players/profile?id=5471&cc=4716 |title=Dave Kitson Bio |publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]soccernet |date= |accessdate=2009-11-18 |archive-date=2010-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100424041659/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/players/profile?id=5471&cc=4716 |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2008年1月傑臣對足總盃作出惹來爭議的評論，他說：『我們不打算贏得足總盃，說真的，我對此毫不在意。』<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2008-01-02 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/reading/7168675.stm |title=FA Cup does not matter - Kitson |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2008-04-13 |archive-date=2008-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080105072035/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/reading/7168675.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。這季傑臣雖然上陣達到36場及射入10球，但雷丁在季尾煞科日確定降班返回英冠。

===史篤城===
2008年7月18日戴夫·傑臣以破球會轉會費紀錄的550萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]由[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]轉投[[英超|英超]]升班馬[[史篤城|史篤城]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7511777.stm |title=Stoke seal £5.5m Kitson transfer |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-18 |accessdate=2009-03-10 |archive-date=2009-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090519094827/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7511777.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。但直到季中戴夫·傑臣仍然未能為史篤城取得一個入球，有傳言他會離隊，但為主席彼得·科茨（{{lang|en|Peter Coates}}）及領隊[[東尼·佩利斯|托尼·帕利斯]]（{{lang|en|Tony Pulis}}）一同否認<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7752488.stm |title=Kitson going nowhere, says Coates |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-11-27 |accessdate=2009-03-10 |archive-date=2009-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205024146/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7752488.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2009年3月10日被外借返回雷丁直到球季結束，如雷丁能夠重返[[英超|英超]]，戴夫·傑臣將會正式留效<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7934235.stm |title=Kitson returns to Reading on loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-10 |accessdate=2009-03-10 |archive-date=2017-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222171907/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7934235.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。重返雷丁的戴夫·傑臣隨即重拾射門鞋，10場上陣射入兩球。隨著雷丁在附加賽準決賽出局，爭取升級失敗後，戴夫·傑臣返回史篤城<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/8049911.stm |title=Kitson set to make Stoke return |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-14 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307134942/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/8049911.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

傑臣表示希望在史篤城從新開始<small><ref>{{cite news|language=en |url=http://www.stokecityfc.com/page/NewsDetail/0,,10310~1728883,00.html |title=Dave's Determined |work=Stoke City FC |publisher=Stoke City |date=15 August 2009 |accessdate=16 August 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090725032529/http://www.stokecityfc.com/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10310~1728883%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-07-25}}</ref></small>，而季初他亦表現出色，於2009年8月26日在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]1-0淘汰[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:莱顿东方;zh-hk:奧連特}-]]取得加盟以來首個競賽性入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/8214952.stm |title=Leyton Orient 0-1 Stoke |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=26 August 2009 |accessdate=27 August 2009 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822032244/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/8214952.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；三天後聯賽主場對[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]，他再一箭定江山，協助球隊1-0獲勝兼在聯賽「開齋」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8223452.stm |title=Stoke 1-0 Sunderland |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=29 August 2009 |accessdate=19 September 2009 |archive-date=2021-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610070057/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8223452.stm }}</ref></small>；9月19日作客對[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]再入1球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8256795.stm |title=Bolton 1-1 Stoke |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=19 September 2009 |accessdate=19 September 2009}}</ref></small>。雖然獲得領隊東尼·佩利斯點名稱讚<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/stoke/article6814821.ece |title= Tony Pulis delighted with Dave Kitson resurgence |publisher=[[The_Times|''timesonline.co.uk'']] |date=2009-08-30 |accessdate=2009-11-18}}</ref></small>，但他在史篤城鋒線仍然排在[[Ricardo_Fuller|-{zh-hans:里卡多·弗勒; zh-hk:富拿;}-]]（Ricardo Fuller）及[[比亞堤|-{zh-hans:詹姆斯·比蒂; zh-hk:比亞堤;}-]]之後，加上季初來投的[[通恰伊·桑利|-{zh-hans:通恰伊; zh-hk:端基;}-]]，傑臣上陣的機會更加減少，於11月17日獲外借到[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]兩個月<small><ref>{{cite news|language=en |url=http://www.stokecityfc.com/page/NewsDetail/0,,10310~1877556,00.html |title=Kitson Completes Loan Move To Boro |publisher=Stoke City FC |date=17 November 2009 |accessdate=17 November 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091120195320/http://www.stokecityfc.com/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10310~1877556%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-11-20}}</ref></small>。

===樸茨茅夫===
2011年夏季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉前傑臣和隊友[[利亚姆·劳伦斯|-{zh-hans:利亚姆·劳伦斯; zh-hk:羅倫士;}-]]（Liam Lawrence）被用作交換籌碼，被史篤城送到[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]換回[[Marc_Wilson_(Irish_footballer)|马克·威尔逊]]（Marc Wilson），傑臣簽約三年<ref>{{cite news|language=en |url=http://www.portsmouthfc.co.uk/LatestNews/news/Kitson-and-Lawrence-In-Wilson-Out-1318.aspx |title=Kitson and Lawrence In Wilson Out |publisher=[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|''portsmouthfc.co.uk'']] |date=2010-08-31 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100903004930/http://www.portsmouthfc.co.uk/LatestNews/news/Kitson-and-Lawrence-In-Wilson-Out-1318.aspx |archivedate=2010-09-03 }}</ref>。隨著樸茨茅夫再次進行債務重組而被財務接管，於2012年降班[[英甲|英甲]]後更要清洗整體一隊球員以避免[[清盤|清盤]]，傑臣於8月3日與樸茨茅夫解約，效力期間上陣72場及射入12球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19120241 |title=Portsmouth: Two left as Dave Kitson leaves Fratton Park |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-08-03 |accessdate=2012-11-17 |archive-date=2012-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106042933/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19120241 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===錫菲聯===
2012年8月31日傑臣以短約形式加盟[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]，簽約至12月31日<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19447128 |title=Sheffield United sign ex-Portsmouth striker Dave Kitson |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-08-31 |accessdate=2012-11-17 |archive-date=2012-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120903044418/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19447128 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於上陣9場射入3球，協助球隊進佔聯賽榜次席後，錫菲聯於11月16日與傑臣延長合約至球季結束，並可優先續約1年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20369237 |title=Dave Kitson extends Sheffield United contract |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-11-16 |accessdate=2012-11-17 |archive-date=2012-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121130004712/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20369237 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

